WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.149
Hey, good evening, everybody. I just wanted

00:00:02.159 --> 00:00:03.470
to come on here and talk to you all

00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:04.970
about some things the Lord has been

00:00:04.980 --> 00:00:06.889
speaking to me about through prayer.

00:00:06.899 --> 00:00:08.450
First off, I want to just

00:00:08.460 --> 00:00:10.250
say thank you for all the support that

00:00:10.260 --> 00:00:12.890
I'm getting, all the encouragement, and all

00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:14.749
the blessings—you all keep saying

00:00:14.759 --> 00:00:16.430
'bless you'and all that stuff. There

00:00:16.430 --> 00:00:16.440
are

00:00:16.440 --> 00:00:18.529
several people who are

00:00:18.539 --> 00:00:20.450
not being too nice, but for the most part,

00:00:20.460 --> 00:00:22.310
I have a lot of support, so I just wanted

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:24.650
to say thank you. I am not a fortune

00:00:24.660 --> 00:00:27.710
teller. Please do not email my house

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:30.230
asking for direction concerning your

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:32.389
life for me to hear God for you.

00:00:32.399 --> 00:00:35.209
My job is to come on here and teach

00:00:35.219 --> 00:00:37.850
you how to do it yourself. You have the

00:00:37.860 --> 00:00:40.069
same Holy Ghost that lives on the inside

00:00:40.079 --> 00:00:42.229
of you that lives on the inside of me.

00:00:42.239 --> 00:00:44.090
People are really concerned about

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:45.830
the EMP attack; people are really

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:47.569
concerned about

00:00:47.579 --> 00:00:52.670
the water poisoning.

00:00:52.680 --> 00:00:54.950
Whenever I was taking care of my yard

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:58.130
work, the Lord spoke to me and

00:00:58.140 --> 00:01:00.110
said there's a shifting.

00:01:00.120 --> 00:01:02.450
I could feel it; there's a pushback of

00:01:02.460 --> 00:01:04.009
the demonic

00:01:04.019 --> 00:01:07.670
assignment that was upon America. Our

00:01:07.680 --> 00:01:10.010
prayers are working, and he reminded me,

00:01:10.020 --> 00:01:12.649
'Brandon, I called you and put you

00:01:12.659 --> 00:01:15.170
on there for prayer.'That was your main

00:01:15.180 --> 00:01:17.330
assignment: to teach the people to pray,

00:01:17.340 --> 00:01:19.969
putting videos of prayer so that they

00:01:19.979 --> 00:01:21.649
could jump in the rivers.

00:01:21.659 --> 00:01:25.130
We are a mighty force together when we

00:01:25.140 --> 00:01:28.609
are praying as a unit, not like, as I

00:01:28.619 --> 00:01:30.890
said, Rambos out there

00:01:30.900 --> 00:01:32.870
trying to fight the war by

00:01:32.870 --> 00:01:32.880
themselves.

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:35.690
If we will come together and fight

00:01:35.700 --> 00:01:38.749
together, we're able to move mountains,

00:01:38.749 --> 00:01:38.759
and

00:01:38.759 --> 00:01:42.170
it's amazing what we can accomplish

00:01:42.180 --> 00:01:44.630
just with five minutes of prayer a day.

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:46.969
I'm not bringing it in, as I said, for

00:01:46.979 --> 00:01:49.789
fear; I'm bringing this to you to help me

00:01:49.799 --> 00:01:53.330
pray. It's not drama. So, here you

00:01:53.340 --> 00:01:55.550
go: I want to come on here and I want to

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:56.990
tell you all some things now about what

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:58.310
the Lord is showing me in prayer. First

00:01:58.320 --> 00:02:00.530
off, I want to tell you all some

00:02:00.540 --> 00:02:02.210
positive things, something that happened

00:02:02.220 --> 00:02:04.130
that was a birthday present to me from

00:02:04.140 --> 00:02:06.590
the Lord. When I was praying, all of a

00:02:06.600 --> 00:02:07.730
sudden, he said, 'I want to give you a

00:02:07.740 --> 00:02:10.190
birthday present, Brandon.'And I said, 'Oh,

00:02:10.200 --> 00:02:12.350
wow, what is it, Lord?'Then all of a

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:14.990
sudden, he opened my eyes in the

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:17.930
spirit and he showed me right after the

00:02:17.940 --> 00:02:21.350
Rapture happens. I was standing in

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:22.610
heaven,

00:02:22.620 --> 00:02:25.309
and I was on this green field. It was

00:02:25.319 --> 00:02:28.369
beautiful. There were hills all

00:02:28.379 --> 00:02:30.770
up in front of me and I could see

00:02:30.780 --> 00:02:33.290
mountains all in the distance. There was

00:02:33.300 --> 00:02:35.510
snow on top of these mountains, which is

00:02:35.520 --> 00:02:36.890
really amazing. This was

00:02:36.890 --> 00:02:36.900
happening—it

00:02:36.900 --> 00:02:39.530
looked like the Swiss Alps.

00:02:39.540 --> 00:02:43.610
It was gorgeous all in the distance.

00:02:43.620 --> 00:02:45.830
These green pastures were

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:49.610
all before me. The grass was so green it

00:02:49.620 --> 00:02:51.410
looked

00:02:51.420 --> 00:02:54.710
almost transparent. It was beautiful

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:57.470
green grass. I have never seen this kind

00:02:57.480 --> 00:02:59.990
of grass on the earth, how beautiful and

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:02.809
lush and green this was. My wife was

00:03:02.819 --> 00:03:05.330
running in from the distance and she was

00:03:05.340 --> 00:03:07.550
doing cartwheels. We were in our

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:09.830
glorified bodies. I could see I was

00:03:09.840 --> 00:03:13.509
skinny and I had hair,

00:03:13.519 --> 00:03:17.030
but my face didn't look hard, as

00:03:17.030 --> 00:03:17.040
if

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:19.430
I'd been through a lot. It was

00:03:19.440 --> 00:03:22.070
so young and youthful; it was

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:25.369
beautiful. Everything I was

00:03:25.369 --> 00:03:25.379
seeing—I

00:03:25.379 --> 00:03:26.690
could see my wife, and she was doing

00:03:26.700 --> 00:03:28.970
cartwheels like I said. She ran into

00:03:28.980 --> 00:03:31.130
me and she goes, 'Brandon, we made it! It

00:03:31.140 --> 00:03:33.649
really happened.'And I kept saying, 'It

00:03:33.659 --> 00:03:35.690
really happened. We made it.'I could

00:03:35.700 --> 00:03:37.850
see the glory; you could feel the

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:40.130
presence of glory. There were no shadows

00:03:40.140 --> 00:03:42.890
on anything; the light was so beautiful

00:03:42.900 --> 00:03:44.869
and so bright.

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:46.729
Sorry, my dog is running in the back playing

00:03:46.729 --> 00:03:46.739
with a

00:03:46.739 --> 00:03:47.809
toy, if you heard that

00:03:47.819 --> 00:03:48.830
squeaking.

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:50.750
There was a glorious

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:54.550
light all around everything and

00:03:54.560 --> 00:03:57.229
heaven. I just wanted to come on

00:03:57.239 --> 00:04:00.050
and tell you all, we're about to be

00:04:00.060 --> 00:04:02.270
there. We're almost there; we're right

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:04.070
at the finish line, guys. We just got

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:06.110
to push just a little bit harder here. We

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:07.850
got to pray, and God's going to do some

00:04:07.860 --> 00:04:09.890
great things in this earth still with a

00:04:09.900 --> 00:04:11.449
revival. There's going to be some people

00:04:11.459 --> 00:04:13.070
He's going to bring in that have been

00:04:13.070 --> 00:04:13.080
wayward—the

00:04:13.080 --> 00:04:14.929
children that are wayward.

00:04:14.939 --> 00:04:16.729
Like I said, the moms are

00:04:16.739 --> 00:04:18.289
praying, and they're calling out

00:04:18.299 --> 00:04:19.969
and asking God for their kids to get

00:04:19.979 --> 00:04:22.189
born again. I'm telling you, don't give up

00:04:22.189 --> 00:04:22.199
on

00:04:22.199 --> 00:04:24.290
those children

00:04:24.300 --> 00:04:26.870
that are wayward. The Lord hears your

00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:28.670
prayers, and He's bringing those kids in.

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:30.650
I'm telling you, you just got to keep the

00:04:30.660 --> 00:04:32.570
faith and keep standing, and there's

00:04:32.580 --> 00:04:34.010
going to be a breakthrough in your

00:04:34.020 --> 00:04:36.230
household. I'm telling you, you just got

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:38.629
to keep on. When all else there

00:04:38.629 --> 00:04:38.639
is

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:41.450
to do is stand, stand therefore. Do not

00:04:41.460 --> 00:04:42.530
give up

00:04:42.540 --> 00:04:44.870
for your healings, for the miracles

00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:47.090
that you're believing for, or for

00:04:47.100 --> 00:04:49.249
finances. You may not have anything to

00:04:49.259 --> 00:04:51.710
eat, but my God said He's never seen the

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:53.810
righteous forsaken or his seed begging

00:04:53.820 --> 00:04:55.909
bread. He'll bring forth the finances

00:04:55.919 --> 00:04:57.469
that you need.

00:04:57.479 --> 00:05:00.469
I just believe in a faithful God; if He

00:05:00.479 --> 00:05:03.350
would bring the raven to feed Elijah,

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:05.810
He'll bring a raven to feed

00:05:05.820 --> 00:05:07.249
you.

00:05:07.259 --> 00:05:10.310
Now, I just want to tell you all what

00:05:10.320 --> 00:05:12.530
the Lord has warned me about what's

00:05:12.540 --> 00:05:14.870
coming and what we can avoid in prayer

00:05:14.880 --> 00:05:18.010
and what we can stop.

00:05:18.020 --> 00:05:20.150
Excuse me,

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:23.749
I saw...

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:25.850
this is something that

00:05:25.850 --> 00:05:25.860
reminded

00:05:25.860 --> 00:05:28.370
me when I was doing my yard

00:05:28.380 --> 00:05:29.450
work tonight. This is what I'm trying to

00:05:29.460 --> 00:05:31.490
tell you. He said, 'I want you to tell

00:05:31.500 --> 00:05:34.010
them to pray for Donald Trump.'I saw him

00:05:34.020 --> 00:05:37.610
walking down on a cobblestone path. I saw

00:05:37.620 --> 00:05:39.650
it was like tropical—I don't know where

00:05:39.660 --> 00:05:43.370
he was—but I saw a woman. Now, sometimes

00:05:43.380 --> 00:05:45.710
I'm seeing in the spirit and it's not

00:05:45.720 --> 00:05:48.529
necessarily... this

00:05:48.539 --> 00:05:51.230
warning that the

00:05:51.240 --> 00:05:53.330
Lord has told me about was about

00:05:53.340 --> 00:05:55.850
Donald Trump and to intercede and

00:05:55.860 --> 00:05:57.409
pray for him.

00:05:57.419 --> 00:06:01.070
He showed me him walking down a

00:06:01.080 --> 00:06:04.370
cobblestone path. Now, I don't know

00:06:04.380 --> 00:06:07.370
if this is legitimately a cobblestone

00:06:07.380 --> 00:06:09.290
path or if

00:06:09.300 --> 00:06:11.029
it's like a type and shadow of something.

00:06:11.039 --> 00:06:14.150
He's walking down this path, and

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:16.370
this woman is

00:06:16.380 --> 00:06:18.590
absolutely beautiful. She

00:06:18.590 --> 00:06:18.600
has

00:06:18.600 --> 00:06:20.870
blonde hair in a French twist

00:06:20.880 --> 00:06:22.969
and she was dressed

00:06:22.979 --> 00:06:26.390
up in a beautiful dress. She

00:06:26.400 --> 00:06:29.749
was there to take him out.

00:06:29.759 --> 00:06:32.930
The Secret

00:06:32.940 --> 00:06:34.850
Service people around were

00:06:34.860 --> 00:06:37.610
not guarded because of this

00:06:37.620 --> 00:06:40.370
woman's beauty; she was very

00:06:40.380 --> 00:06:43.129
classy. I don't know if this is a

00:06:43.139 --> 00:06:44.930
type and shadow of someone

00:06:44.930 --> 00:06:44.940
who

00:06:44.940 --> 00:06:47.390
would try to

00:06:47.400 --> 00:06:49.490
seduce him,

00:06:49.500 --> 00:06:51.950
but this woman was an assignment

00:06:51.960 --> 00:06:55.189
against him. This

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:56.450
is something I'm praying

00:06:56.460 --> 00:06:59.330
over: protection for God to deliver

00:06:59.340 --> 00:07:02.809
him from either a seducing spirit, like a

00:07:02.819 --> 00:07:05.570
Jezebel kind of person, or an actual

00:07:05.580 --> 00:07:08.029
attempt on him.

00:07:08.039 --> 00:07:09.770
This is very serious. The Lord has

00:07:09.780 --> 00:07:11.870
had me praying for his protection

00:07:11.870 --> 00:07:11.880
from

00:07:11.880 --> 00:07:14.330
an assignment

00:07:14.330 --> 00:07:14.340
involving

00:07:14.340 --> 00:07:16.670
this beautiful woman. She has blonde hair

00:07:16.680 --> 00:07:19.550
and

00:07:19.560 --> 00:07:23.510
looks very much like

00:07:23.510 --> 00:07:23.520
a

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:25.670
model.

00:07:25.670 --> 00:07:25.680
This

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:27.589
was part of something

00:07:27.599 --> 00:07:28.969
the Lord had me interceding for.

00:07:28.969 --> 00:07:28.979
Lately,

00:07:28.979 --> 00:07:31.790
He had me praying for

00:07:33.599 --> 00:07:36.950
this oil tanker that was in the Atlantic

00:07:36.960 --> 00:07:40.189
Ocean coming out of Africa.

00:07:40.199 --> 00:07:42.170
This is something else; it's

00:07:42.180 --> 00:07:44.029
not about fear, it's just something

00:07:44.039 --> 00:07:46.790
I pray over. You are

00:07:46.790 --> 00:07:46.800
prayer

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:48.909
warriors,

00:07:48.919 --> 00:07:51.650
and you can help me. This

00:07:51.660 --> 00:07:53.150
could be something way off in

00:07:53.150 --> 00:07:53.160
the

00:07:53.160 --> 00:07:54.170
distance or something

00:07:54.180 --> 00:07:56.330
we've already stopped, but I bring

00:07:56.340 --> 00:07:58.850
these things out here. If you feel

00:07:58.860 --> 00:08:01.129
led to pray over it, pray; if not,

00:08:01.139 --> 00:08:03.409
put it on a shelf and walk away. This was

00:08:03.419 --> 00:08:07.010
an oil tanker coming out of Africa, and

00:08:07.020 --> 00:08:10.430
all of the crew on board were

00:08:10.430 --> 00:08:10.440
rounded

00:08:10.440 --> 00:08:12.890
up by these terrorists.

00:08:12.900 --> 00:08:14.689
They were hiding on the ship,

00:08:14.699 --> 00:08:16.610
got on board, took

00:08:16.620 --> 00:08:18.350
these men to the bottom of the ship,

00:08:18.360 --> 00:08:20.089
and killed them.

00:08:20.099 --> 00:08:24.589
I saw them with

00:08:24.589 --> 00:08:24.599
a briefcase—I'm

00:08:24.599 --> 00:08:26.450
not going to say the

00:08:26.450 --> 00:08:26.460
word—but

00:08:26.460 --> 00:08:29.270
it's very

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:31.249
powerful.

00:08:31.259 --> 00:08:34.310
They took the ship

00:08:34.310 --> 00:08:34.320
to

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:38.750
Washington Harbor,

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:41.209
near

00:08:41.219 --> 00:08:43.909
Virginia. I'm going to show you on a map

00:08:43.919 --> 00:08:45.590
right now.

00:08:48.060 --> 00:08:51.410
They brought the ship in and

00:08:51.420 --> 00:08:53.990
set this thing off.

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:56.690
It was very serious

00:08:56.700 --> 00:08:59.150
and powerful;

00:08:59.160 --> 00:09:02.150
everything

00:09:02.160 --> 00:09:04.310
went away. I'm trying to

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:06.350
say this in a way that doesn't get me

00:09:06.360 --> 00:09:09.050
flagged. I just wanted

00:09:09.060 --> 00:09:10.670
to come on here and

00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:12.530
tell you these are more things

00:09:12.540 --> 00:09:14.870
I'm praying over.

00:09:14.880 --> 00:09:18.710
We live in dangerous

00:09:18.710 --> 00:09:18.720
and

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:20.990
challenging times. I do

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:23.329
not live in a fairytale land

00:09:23.329 --> 00:09:23.339
where

00:09:23.339 --> 00:09:26.150
everything is always okay.

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:28.610
I wake up every day and

00:09:28.620 --> 00:09:31.430
the Lord has me on assignments. I am

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:34.190
on missions, praying for things on a

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:36.769
continual basis for what He has for the

00:09:36.779 --> 00:09:39.170
end times, for the church, and

00:09:39.170 --> 00:09:39.180
for

00:09:39.180 --> 00:09:43.310
the thousand years. We

00:09:43.320 --> 00:09:45.949
have a bright future ahead of us; God has

00:09:45.959 --> 00:09:49.070
a great plan for us.

00:09:49.070 --> 00:09:49.080
Lastly,

00:09:49.080 --> 00:09:52.070
He had me pray against large

00:09:52.080 --> 00:09:54.730
gatherings of people

00:09:54.740 --> 00:10:00.050
for mass shootings.

00:10:00.050 --> 00:10:00.060
Pray

00:10:00.060 --> 00:10:02.810
against this; it's an

00:10:02.820 --> 00:10:06.350
assignment being sent to try

00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:08.810
to take the Second Amendment away from

00:10:08.820 --> 00:10:12.650
the people. And they're going to

00:10:12.660 --> 00:10:17.930
run on campaigns in 2024; a lot of it

00:10:17.940 --> 00:10:19.850
will be ran against the Second Amendment

00:10:19.860 --> 00:10:22.130
and taking things away.

00:10:22.140 --> 00:10:25.850
I saw these big mass events

00:10:25.860 --> 00:10:27.829
trying to take place. The Lord had me

00:10:27.839 --> 00:10:30.829
pray very hard for Coachella. I kept

00:10:30.839 --> 00:10:32.269
praying for this word,

00:10:32.269 --> 00:10:32.279
'Coachella,'and

00:10:32.279 --> 00:10:34.490
I kept getting this in the

00:10:34.500 --> 00:10:36.410
spirit realm. So I told my friend about

00:10:36.420 --> 00:10:37.970
it and he helped me Google it, and then

00:10:37.980 --> 00:10:40.070
my wife helped me Google this word.

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:42.470
It was days away from what was

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:44.509
supposed to take place, and I interceded

00:10:44.519 --> 00:10:48.170
for this hard. I prayed a

00:10:48.170 --> 00:10:48.180
fast,

00:10:48.180 --> 00:10:50.389
believing God for protection so that this

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:52.490
stuff didn't happen. Nothing happened. Now,

00:10:52.500 --> 00:10:54.110
I don't know when it happens again; I

00:10:54.120 --> 00:10:56.449
believe probably next year. So we're

00:10:56.459 --> 00:10:58.910
going to pray that these major events

00:10:58.910 --> 00:10:58.920
and

00:10:58.920 --> 00:11:01.970
big gatherings of people for nothing to

00:11:01.980 --> 00:11:05.690
happen. If you have a check in

00:11:05.700 --> 00:11:08.509
your spirit about major gatherings, do

00:11:08.519 --> 00:11:11.870
not go. Pray in the Holy Ghost and the

00:11:11.880 --> 00:11:13.430
Lord will protect you.

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:16.610
Use wisdom in this day and hour for you

00:11:16.610 --> 00:11:16.620
and

00:11:16.620 --> 00:11:19.670
for your family to not just be

00:11:19.680 --> 00:11:22.550
flippantly going places.

00:11:22.560 --> 00:11:25.790
Pray ahead of time: 'Lord, is it Your will

00:11:25.800 --> 00:11:28.190
for me to go to that concert? Is it Your

00:11:28.200 --> 00:11:31.370
will for me to go to that sporting

00:11:31.370 --> 00:11:31.380
event?'Because

00:11:31.380 --> 00:11:33.230
if you don't and you

00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:35.389
hear the Lord not to go,

00:11:35.399 --> 00:11:37.790
it could cost you your life. You have to

00:11:37.800 --> 00:11:41.389
be very vigilant nowadays in prayer and

00:11:41.399 --> 00:11:44.210
fasting, listening to Him on where you're

00:11:44.220 --> 00:11:46.850
supposed to be at all times. Don't just

00:11:46.860 --> 00:11:48.590
go to malls; do not just go to

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:50.630
certain things without hearing Him on

00:11:50.630 --> 00:11:50.640
that

00:11:50.640 --> 00:11:52.310
day. Wake up that morning and say,

00:11:52.320 --> 00:11:54.949
'Father, what am I supposed to do? What's

00:11:54.959 --> 00:11:57.530
Your agenda for me, not what's my agenda?'You

00:11:57.530 --> 00:11:57.540
listen to

00:11:57.540 --> 00:11:59.630
Him

00:11:59.640 --> 00:12:02.150
for your life.

00:12:02.160 --> 00:12:04.850
'Lord, can I go to the grocery store

00:12:04.860 --> 00:12:07.550
today? Can I go to the

00:12:07.560 --> 00:12:09.829
game? Can I go to this and

00:12:09.839 --> 00:12:10.970
that?'Ask

00:12:10.980 --> 00:12:14.569
Him; He will guide you on every step

00:12:14.579 --> 00:12:16.910
you're supposed to take for your life

00:12:16.920 --> 00:12:19.550
that day, every day.

00:12:19.560 --> 00:12:21.769
He wants to be that close to

00:12:21.779 --> 00:12:24.290
you. Let Him speak to you and practice His

00:12:24.300 --> 00:12:26.030
presence.

00:12:26.040 --> 00:12:28.430
A lot of people always ask me,

00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:31.250
'How do you hear God the way you do? How

00:12:31.260 --> 00:12:33.290
do you listen to Him like

00:12:33.290 --> 00:12:33.300
that?'It

00:12:33.300 --> 00:12:36.170
started like this.

00:12:36.180 --> 00:12:38.150
He told me, 'I'm going to start

00:12:38.160 --> 00:12:40.250
talking to you about things, and I want

00:12:40.260 --> 00:12:42.530
you to practice My voice. I want you

00:12:42.540 --> 00:12:44.930
to practice this.'It was just private

00:12:44.940 --> 00:12:47.030
between me and Him, and He said, 'I'm going

00:12:47.040 --> 00:12:48.410
to tell you about

00:12:48.410 --> 00:12:48.420
sports

00:12:48.420 --> 00:12:51.530
because I love sports.'It's one of my big

00:12:51.530 --> 00:12:51.540
things—football,

00:12:51.540 --> 00:12:54.769
basketball, baseball, all

00:12:54.779 --> 00:12:56.569
of it. I watch it, I love it, it's amazing

00:12:56.579 --> 00:12:58.610
to me. You know, just the game; I love the

00:12:58.620 --> 00:13:01.970
testosterone of it. And so,

00:13:01.980 --> 00:13:03.949
we would sit on the couch together, the

00:13:03.959 --> 00:13:06.910
Lord and I, and He would talk to me about

00:13:06.920 --> 00:13:10.490
the score. He'd say, 'This is who's

00:13:10.500 --> 00:13:12.530
going to win, and this is the score, and this is how

00:13:12.540 --> 00:13:14.090
much they're going to win

00:13:14.090 --> 00:13:14.100
by—this

00:13:14.100 --> 00:13:15.470
team and this team.'He'd tell me the

00:13:15.480 --> 00:13:16.850
game for that day, college football

00:13:16.850 --> 00:13:16.860
or

00:13:16.860 --> 00:13:18.829
whatever, and He said, 'This is who's going

00:13:18.839 --> 00:13:20.449
to win it, and this is how much they're

00:13:20.459 --> 00:13:22.009
going to win it by.'He talked about Super

00:13:22.019 --> 00:13:24.350
Bowls, He talks about World Series, He

00:13:24.360 --> 00:13:27.110
talks about it all. And so I practice His

00:13:27.120 --> 00:13:29.090
presence; I practice His voice.

00:13:29.100 --> 00:13:31.009
He said to me, 'If

00:13:31.019 --> 00:13:34.730
you ever bet or gamble on anything I

00:13:34.740 --> 00:13:36.829
ever tell you, I will not talk this way

00:13:36.839 --> 00:13:39.410
to you ever again. But I want you to

00:13:39.410 --> 00:13:39.420
go

00:13:39.420 --> 00:13:41.449
like you're going to a

00:13:41.459 --> 00:13:44.110
spiritual gym. I want you to work out

00:13:44.120 --> 00:13:46.730
that muscle, your

00:13:46.740 --> 00:13:49.190
spiritual ears, with

00:13:49.190 --> 00:13:49.200
Me.'And

00:13:49.200 --> 00:13:51.829
this is how I started: I practice His

00:13:51.839 --> 00:13:54.050
presence. Then He talks to me about the

00:13:54.060 --> 00:13:57.530
weather. He says, 'In six weeks, it's going

00:13:57.530 --> 00:13:57.540
to

00:13:57.540 --> 00:14:00.290
be this temperature outside;

00:14:00.300 --> 00:14:01.910
it's going to snow, and this is how much we're going

00:14:01.910 --> 00:14:01.920
to get.'He

00:14:01.920 --> 00:14:03.829
talks to me about how much rain we're going

00:14:03.829 --> 00:14:03.839
to

00:14:03.839 --> 00:14:05.990
get. He talks to me about when the

00:14:06.000 --> 00:14:07.490
fall will start, when the first cold

00:14:07.500 --> 00:14:10.129
front's going to come, and He tells me way

00:14:10.139 --> 00:14:11.449
in advance. He said, 'I want you to

00:14:11.459 --> 00:14:13.370
write this down.'He said summer's going

00:14:13.370 --> 00:14:13.380
to

00:14:13.380 --> 00:14:15.470
have this many hurricanes, and in

00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:17.449
the Gulf Coast, this is how many

00:14:17.459 --> 00:14:19.430
hurricanes are going to be here and this is

00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:21.230
how big they're going to be. You can pray

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:22.910
against them, pray for safety for people,

00:14:22.920 --> 00:14:25.190
and He will show me. Then He shows me

00:14:25.200 --> 00:14:27.410
about tornado season; He shows me about

00:14:27.420 --> 00:14:29.990
the storms. That's how I've learned

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:32.650
to develop my spiritual ears,

00:14:32.660 --> 00:14:35.569
practicing His presence. And sometimes

00:14:35.579 --> 00:14:37.610
you miss it. It's okay;

00:14:37.620 --> 00:14:40.129
we're human. But you just keep picking

00:14:40.139 --> 00:14:41.750
yourself back up and say, 'Lord, I missed

00:14:41.760 --> 00:14:43.370
that. I thought I

00:14:43.380 --> 00:14:45.050
heard You right on that, but I

00:14:45.050 --> 00:14:45.060
didn't.'And

00:14:45.060 --> 00:14:46.970
you humble yourself and you keep

00:14:46.980 --> 00:14:48.949
going. You don't kick

00:14:48.959 --> 00:14:51.110
yourself when you fall down; you rise

00:14:51.120 --> 00:14:52.670
back up.

00:14:52.680 --> 00:14:55.430
You have to keep on keeping on.

00:14:56.579 --> 00:14:58.730
We all have a tendency; we can miss it.

00:14:58.740 --> 00:14:59.990
I'm going to tell you

00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:02.269
right off: I've missed it a lot on

00:15:02.279 --> 00:15:04.610
things when I was first starting out,

00:15:04.620 --> 00:15:06.530
about investments and the timing of things,

00:15:09.530 --> 00:15:09.540
and

00:15:10.620 --> 00:15:13.370
it's okay. That's how we learn.

00:15:13.380 --> 00:15:15.829
I just want to encourage

00:15:15.839 --> 00:15:18.170
you all.

00:15:18.180 --> 00:15:21.230
God is a graceful God. He's not mad;

00:15:21.240 --> 00:15:23.810
he's not up there beating people up. He

00:15:23.810 --> 00:15:23.820
is

00:15:23.820 --> 00:15:26.750
a lot of love. I just

00:15:26.760 --> 00:15:28.430
wanted to encourage you with that. That

00:15:28.440 --> 00:15:29.990
was another thing I wanted to tell you.

00:15:30.000 --> 00:15:34.459
Have a blessed day, everybody. Bye-bye.

